  <Dialog id="0" name="MSG_000_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 1 0 0}...!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="1" name="MSG_001_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 2 0 0}I'm so glad you're awake.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="2" name="MSG_002_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 3 0 0}Chidori...?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="3" name="MSG_003_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 4 0 0}Huh? I thought I was...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="4" name="MSG_004_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 5 0 0}I guess... I was wrong.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="5" name="MSG_005_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 6 0 0}My fear, my heartache... I blamed it all on you, Junpei.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 7 0 0}I'd never felt that way before I met you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}And for the first time in my life, I...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}I realized what I wanted.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="7" name="MSG_007_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 10 0 0}And... what's that?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="8" name="MSG_008_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 11 0 0}I... want to be with you, Junpei. Forever.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="9" name="MSG_009_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 1 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 12 0 0}I, um, uh...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 1 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 13 0 0}I-I... I wanna be with you, too.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="10" name="MSG_010_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 14 0 0}But it could never last... And it breaks my heart.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}We're different from you.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 16 0 0}Since the moment I gained my power, I've known the day I was going to die.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="11" name="MSG_011_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 0 0 0 17 0 0}Huh!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="12" name="MSG_012_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 18 0 0}The very thought of it horrified me.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 19 0 0}Up until then, I'd never once thought about death.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 3 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 20 0 0}But I realize now dying means I won't see you anymore.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="13" name="MSG_013_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 0 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 21 0 0}Chidori...[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="14" name="MSG_014_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 22 0 0}That's why... this is for the best.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0001"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 213 1 -1 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 23 0 0}You can't die here, Junpei.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="15" name="MSG_015_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 24 0 0}Me... Die?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="16" name="MSG_016_0_0" type="Message">
    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 4 2 11 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 25 0 0}Wha—!?[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
